    "# 05: Benchmark Results\n",
    "\n",
    "Report performance on all 12 benchmark tasks from Radford's paper.\n",
    "\n",
    "Expected SOTA scores (Table 4):\n",
    "- CoLA: 45.4 (vs 93.2/91.3 baseline)\n",
    "- SST-2: 91.3 (vs 90.2 baseline)\n",
    "- MRPC: 82.3 (vs 80.2 baseline)\n",
    "- STSB: 82.0 (vs 55.5 baseline)\n",
    "- QQP: 70.3 (vs 66.1 baseline)\n",
    "- MNLI: 82.1 (vs 72.2 baseline)\n",
    "- QNLI: 81.4 (vs 75.7 baseline)\n",
    "- SNLI: 89.9 (vs 88.5 baseline)\n",
    "- RACE: 57.4 (vs 55.6 baseline)\n",
    "- Story Cloze: 86.5 (vs 77.6 baseline)"
   ]
