", " |--------|------------|------|-------|------|------|------|------|------|------|------|------|---------------- |\n",
", " | Transformer w/ aux LM (full) | 74.7 | 45.4 | 91.3 | 82.3 | 82.0 | 70.3 | 81.8 | 88.1 | 56.0 | 62.3 | 86.5 |\n",
", " | Transformer w/o pre-training | 59.9 | 18.9 | 84.0 | 79.4 | 30.9 | 65.5 | 75.7 | 71.2 | 53.8 | 49.4 | 83.6 |\n",
